(1, 0, '2017夏季流行的缎面', '', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px;&quot;&gt;　最近，缎面正在以刷屏的姿势，强势霸占2017年夏季的街头霸主地位，各种单品都充斥着它的身影。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/90/10469409464453972.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图1)&quot; title=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图1)&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; hspace=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; _src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/90/10469409464453972.jpg&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;338&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 5px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 630px; float: none; width: 500px; height: 338px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px;&quot;&gt;　　早在今年年初的春夏流行发布会上，各大秀场就已经把它大面积的搬上台面。自带白富美气息的缎面材质非常优雅有气质，丝滑的触感，细腻的光泽和独特的垂坠感也是苏胡得没话说。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/91/10469454281725972.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图2)&quot; title=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图2)&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; hspace=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; _src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/91/10469454281725972.jpg&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;597&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 5px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 630px; float: none; width: 400px; height: 597px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;　　▲Etro Fashion Show Ready to Wear 2017&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/92/10469590471887972.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图3)&quot; title=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图3)&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; hspace=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; _src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/92/10469590471887972.jpg&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;597&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 5px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 630px; line-height: 1.8em; text-indent: 2em; float: none; width: 400px; height: 597px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;　　▲Hellessy Spring 2017 Ready-to-Wear Fashion Show&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/93/10469651940984972.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图4)&quot; title=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图4)&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; hspace=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; _src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/93/10469651940984972.jpg&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;597&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 5px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 630px; line-height: 1.8em; text-indent: 2em; float: none; width: 400px; height: 597px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;　　▲Monse Spring 2017 Ready-to-Wear Fashion Show&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/94/10469721851460972.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图5)&quot; title=&quot;2017夏季流行的缎面，好看到想哭！！(图5)&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; hspace=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; _src=&quot;http://img1.nz86.com/upload/video/system/19/29/94/10469721851460972.jpg&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;597&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 5px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 630px; float: none; width: 400px; height: 597px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px;&quot;&gt;　　▲今年夏天最高街的睡衣装，宇博自然也要带一波节奏，还在纠结选什么颜色？深蓝色一定是首选。&lt;/p&gt;', 1499999663, 0, 0, 0, 'UploadFiles/news/20170714/1499999663866345.png', '本网');
