(8, 0, '爱尔兰如梦如幻', '', '&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 16px=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; 25=&quot;&quot; 6px=&quot;&quot; widows:=&quot;&quot; 1=&quot;&quot; box-sizing:=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; word-wrap:=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 204, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt;&quot;&gt;许多人对爱尔兰的印象，多来自于抽象的地理概念，这个位于欧洲最西端的岛国东隔爱尔兰海同英国相望。真实的爱尔兰却要精彩得多，那里有有故事的海岸景观道、鬼斧神工的地质奇观、令人回味的健力士黑啤，还有频繁面对时而小雨时而晴的鬼天气、仍感叹生活美好的爱尔兰人&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 204, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt;&quot;&gt;……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p&quot; align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;　　有人说，爱尔兰是个无法预测的国度。为什么要预测呢？就该像爱尔兰人那样抛下顾虑，随心而行.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;随心而行爱尔兰&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　嘀哒、嘀哒、嘀哒……敞篷马车在宁静的基拉尼国家公园里缓慢而行，空气里弥漫着甜甜的花香，身边的树叶呈现出或红或黄或绿的色彩，转个弯，一座茅草屋咖啡馆跃入眼前，咖啡客头都不抬，独自惬意地享受着温暖阳光……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　爱尔兰，这个只有570万人口的岛国里，人均拥有两头羊、两头牛和一头猪。中西部有延绵不断的草地，农场主都自行修建仅一层楼的“小洋房”和可以开车通往公路的小径，牛羊们优雅地在路边的草地上遐思，大巴经过时，它们也懒得挪动脚步。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGVqcFrIzo2q0keUDNmkv5qCu7yIknbxDbpzc1tkJqtut0wDp0UbLF9UcL8w4s5p6TzVLnAfJLlCOQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.893491124260355&quot; data-w=&quot;676&quot; src=&quot;http://www.gzleren.com/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251805401891.jpg&quot; data-fail=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;140&quot; height=&quot;140&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　初到爱尔兰，最容易被感动的就是爱尔兰的草场和草场上零星散落的牛羊，爱尔兰号称翡翠之国，重要的不是97%的绿化率世界第一，重要的是其97%的绿化率里面超过90%都是草场。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-f