rd-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　莫赫悬崖的工作人员介绍，当时拍摄《哈利·波特》时，是借助着电影高科技，他们踩的石头取自距离悬崖以南150公里的凯里郡Iveragh半岛柠檬岩石。电影中相关镜头是摄制组2007年9月在莫赫悬崖工作一周后，从直升机上俯拍的场景。洞穴里的镜头是在悬崖岩洞里拍摄的实景，加上后期合成，设计出的虚拟景观。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(43, 201, 143); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;Bunratty &amp;nbsp;Castle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;Bunratty的中世纪晚宴：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;生活就是一场电影&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　这个我们中途停留的地方，不是什么电影的拍摄地，但是，这一晚，过得却好像生活在电影中一样&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　Bunratty城堡是爱尔兰香侬低地另一处著名的胜地。19世纪的贫穷与哀痛远去后，这些复制的农村生活，就变成了解爱尔兰文化的窗口。Bunratty始建于13世纪，创建人是一名叫做托马斯的诺尔曼人。Bunratty是爱尔兰四大城堡中历史最悠久、收藏最丰富的一座，收藏了许多中世纪的家具、挂毯以及武器。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　每天晚上，Bunratty城堡都会举行中世纪晚宴，分上下两场，几乎都是人满为患。晚宴上，所有工作人员都身穿中世纪服饰，宾客们严格按照中世纪的程序用餐，没有刀子，只有一把叉子和手，在通幽的烛光里，听着中世纪时的笑话和情话表演，不时，小提琴悠扬的曲调响起，可以调剂一下当时太过搞笑的氛围，最后，会以合唱结尾，让客人们在优雅的和音中，完成一顿完美的中世纪晚餐。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　“你知道许多来爱尔兰玩的美国人为了能参加这场晚餐，不惜从都柏林飞到这里，用完晚餐再飞回去。”这样对我们说这座城堡的市场推广经理。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 128, 0); text-align: center; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(128, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;艾伦岛&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;爱尔兰的花园威克洛(Wicklow)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;《勇敢的心》、《拯救大兵瑞恩》&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　从都柏林出发，开车两个小时左右，就可以到达被誉为“爱尔兰的花园”的威克洛郡。威克洛拥有这样的称号是有充分理由的，它无穷无尽的绿色树林和壮丽风景，都为各种户外活动提供了完美的自然空间，游客可以尽情骑马、爬山或打高尔夫球。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　这里也诞生了两部最让世人耳熟能详的好莱坞大片《勇敢的心》和《拯救大兵瑞恩》。尤其是由梅尔·吉普森主演、讲述13世纪苏格兰人反抗英格兰统治的故事的《勇敢的心》。电影中不少在原野上战斗和草原上策马的外景，包括大批英格兰的军队与苏格兰的反抗将士对抗的场景，尽在这个叫威克洛的地区取景。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　World2000娱乐有限公司的总裁，也是《勇敢的心》的制片人之一MorganO’Sullivan在接受采访的时候说：很多人都以为《勇敢的心》是在苏格兰取景，跑去找寻才发现“受骗”了。Morgan还有一句相当Slogan的总结：想看苏格兰的美景吗？那么去爱尔兰吧，在这里，你能找到一切。影片中，不仅大量场景拍摄来自爱尔兰，就连群众演员也是来自爱尔兰，甚至动用了爱尔兰的国家军队。而这曾经是梅尔·吉普森的救命草：没有Morgan说服爱尔兰政府动用国家正规军参演，《勇敢的心》几乎要“泡汤”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　爱尔兰有一个特色，就是古堡多。英国统治爱尔兰的900多年里，派驻或册封了很多管理各个地区的领主，这些领主大建城堡作为据点。由于爱尔兰几百年来几乎没有遭遇大的战火，中世纪以来的古堡大都得以完整保存。那些墙壁上爬满绿色植物的城堡所记载的，不仅是一个家族的兴盛与衰败，更是岁月留下的一个个故事&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　《勇敢的心》中屡屡出现的英军城堡，实际是爱尔兰中部的崔姆(TRIM)古堡，这是爱尔兰众多军用建筑中最宏伟也最重要的一座。第一眼，你就会被它的气魄深深打动。建于800年前的基尔肯尼(KILKENY)古堡位于诺尔河边，号称“铜墙铁壁”，城堡呈不规则的四边形，筑有大量的鼓楼。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　在威克洛郡里，有大片大片的平坦的荒野之地，长满了大片大片的天然长草，如果是热爱高尔夫的人，会感叹这里的天然Links地形，几乎无需设计，就是一片不错的高尔夫球场。而很多热爱自然运动的人，最喜欢做的就是骑着自行车或摩托车，在美景中穿越。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　在这里开车闲逛的时候，我们发现了一个叫“好莱坞”的宁静村庄，只有寥寥的几户住家，除了穿行的汽车，几乎看不到人。据导游Kevin说，这个村子在这里存在已经很久了，相当古老，起码几百年的历史，其实跟&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;美国&lt;/span&gt;的&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;洛杉矶&lt;/span&gt;好莱坞完全没有关系的。我倒不禁联想，当年爱尔兰人大量地移民美国，没准就有一个来自好莱坞的村民，让这个名字在漂洋过海的新土地上了扎下了根，并且发扬光大。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGVqcFrIzo2q0keUDNmkv5qCxjtZeWooBbWicsZrKP68Icy6TkJWeACHtvlPDSZhZTDibWa5YVZibArRA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.893491124260355&quot; data-w=&quot;676&quot; src=&quot;http://www.gzleren.com/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251807188507.jpg&quot; data-fail=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;140&quot; height=&quot;140&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(168, 39, 168); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 22px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(168, 39, 168); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;如幻如梦爱尔兰 天生电影布景地&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;爱尔兰恐怕是世界上最适合电影主题之旅的国家，几乎随处都是舞台布景，天然而成绿色幕布和多变气候雕琢出的山脉、大地、岩石？成就了最自然的布景。爱尔兰政府也相当给力：在这片土地上拍摄电影，可以减免所得税。这一招很成功，其他欧洲国家也开始效仿爱尔兰政府的税收奖励计划。经过长期的努力，爱尔兰的电影产业得到了越来越多的投资，这对解决就业相当重要。而最重要的是，电影中那些如幻如梦的场景，正在重新塑造爱尔兰的国家形象。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(43, 201, 143); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;爱尔兰的生活节奏比较慢&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　爱尔兰的生活节奏比较慢。在这个被利菲(Liffey)河分割成两部分的城市中，沿河步行是最好的游览方式。河的两岸是鳞次栉比的酒吧、餐厅、酒店，还有各种用途的古罗马式建筑，每一处都适合停下脚步慢慢欣赏。也许，正是这种“慢”，让生于斯、长于斯的爱尔兰人更静心地体会生活的节律，所以，都柏林是文化的摇篮，孕育了一代又一代的文学家，萧伯纳、叶慈，还有我钟情的王尔德。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　“我亲爱的肮脏的爱尔兰。”站在都柏林湾的乔伊斯圆塔上，望着远处的大海，脑子里还会想起乔伊斯的这句话。这样的悖论让人着迷。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(153, 204, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(153, 204, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(168, 39, 168); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 22px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(168, 39, 168); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;爱尔兰 之 文学作品&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(43, 201, 143); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(43, 201, 143); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; 公元5世纪，基督教传入爱尔兰，直到中世纪初，爱尔兰一直是一个与外界隔绝的基督教学习中心。欧洲大陆黑暗的中世纪，爱尔兰教士便在欧洲各地建立了宗教学习中心，因此爱尔兰又被誉为学者之岛、科学家之岛。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;-webkit-text-stroke: rgb(43, 201, 143); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(43, 201, 143); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;文学对爱尔兰人的生活也产生了重大的影响，如每年6月布&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1501036054, 0, 0, 0, 'UploadFiles/news/20170726/1501036054684555.png', '本网');
