ly: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">苎麻亚麻面料以前一直是作为古欧洲皇室的专用面料，尽在上层社会流通，随着苎麻面料在世界范围内广为流通，苎麻面料的优点也被人们逐渐的发掘出来。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">苎麻的这种天然的透气性、吸湿性、清爽性.抗过敏.防静电.抗菌和排性，使其成为自由呼吸的纺织品，由于苎麻的吸湿性好，能吸收相当于自身重量 20倍的水分，所以苎麻织物手感干爽。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none