(8, 1, 3, '布拉格城堡', '', '', 3600.00, 2520.00, 0, 'UploadFiles/product/20170725/1500976129774168.png', 'UploadFiles/product/20170725/1500976129659744.png', NULL, '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236);">布拉格这个名称来自德语，当地称它为布拉哈，意为“门槛”，其原因是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(45, 100, 179);">伏尔塔瓦河</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236);">在这里流经一个暗礁，水流湍急，酷似越过一个门槛。还有这样一个传说：古时开始建设城市时，建筑师来到这里勘察，他遇见一个老人，正在锯木做门槛，做得异常认真、仔细，建筑师深受感动，城市建成之后，便命名为布拉格</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 19px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 19px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGX0joARs4HTdCkdKGv803cTuGCmGQHf5wJ2VFRp3qsGibbuCTMibPhwvKXjSXaEcVXXSloH3HYSvbzQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.5960099750623442" data-w="802" src="/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251740556829.png" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" width="140" height="140" alt="" width="100%" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">布拉格</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">城堡（Prague Castle），位于<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">捷克</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">伏尔塔瓦河</span>的丘陵上，是捷克的要塞，在公元第九世纪时布拉格的王子首先在伏尔塔瓦﹝Vltava﹞的山上盖了一座城堡，此后他便在此开始统治他的捷克人民和土地，一直是布拉格王室的所在地，几世纪以来经过多次扩建，不仅保留许多雄伟建筑和历史文物，现今仍是捷克总统的居所。布拉格城堡有多样化的建筑风格，从古代的罗马式地基，到战争期间的后现代风格，每个年代的风格都或多或少在城堡上留下了痕迹</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGX0joARs4HTdCkdKGv803cTgSeglStiaQZ3GTKET16diaCBqCuGnHqEEWGK0HnTicPrF1gMzuSiaUUGicw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.5960099750623442" data-w="802" src="/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251743474455.png" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" width="140" height="140" alt="" width="100%" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">这里有罗马式、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">哥特式</span>、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">巴洛克式</span>、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">文艺复兴</span>式等各个历史时代风格的建筑。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(19, 110, 194); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">布拉格城堡图册&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">功能类型包括教堂、王宫、画廊、大厅、塑像、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">喷泉</span>等。其中以文艺复兴时代建的晚期哥特式加冕大厅、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">安娜</span>女皇娱乐厅、西班牙大厅最有名。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">君喜善设计师感触最深的当属圣维塔大教堂</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 19px; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGX0joARs4HTdCkdKGv803cT7Da9WFRia58sjZMkMgSNLP4cEF5JnG5C8YRYjtNdtkGwicPR2MrCdVCw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.6" data-w="800" src="/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251743592401.png" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" width="140" height="140" alt="" width="100%" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">圣维塔大教堂</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">（Katedrala sv. Vita）是布拉格城堡最重要的地标，除了丰富的建筑特色外，也是布拉格城堡王室加冕与辞世后长眠之所。圣维塔大教堂历经3次扩建，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(19, 110, 194); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">圣维塔大教堂</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">公元929年的圣温塞斯拉斯圆形教堂，在公元1060年时扩建为长方形教堂，公元1344年查理四世下令建造，却一直到公元1929年才正式完工。圣维塔大教堂的几个参观重点包括20世纪的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">彩色玻璃</span>窗、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">圣约翰</span>之墓和圣温塞斯拉斯礼拜堂。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">走进教堂入口，左侧色彩鲜丽的彩色玻璃就是布拉格著名画家穆哈的作品，为这个千年历史的教堂增添不少现代感。绕过圣坛后方，纯银打造、装饰华丽的是的圣约翰之墓，他是1736年的反宗教改革者，因此葬在圣维塔大教堂中，并以纯银华丽的装饰作为纪念。 继续往前就是圣温塞斯拉斯礼拜堂，相较于前面纯银的圣约翰之墓，圣温塞斯拉斯礼拜堂呈现出金碧辉煌的光彩，从壁画到圣礼尖塔都有<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">金彩</span>装饰，相当具有艺术价值。从外观来看，哥德式的圣维塔大教堂有许多经典建筑特色，例如拱门上的拱柱和<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: normal; color: rgb(19, 110, 194); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(19, 110, 194);">飞扶壁</span>，都装饰的相当华丽。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">这个系列的灵感就是来自这个拱门</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGX0joARs4HTdCkdKGv803cTdCGUppAVRCLn9LvrGR7EWbQmBibt5LSnFnGksvpbyOCgGwAzibB7xm4A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.6494845360824741" data-w="776" src="/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251744323509.png" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" width="140" height="140" alt="" width="100%" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 150, 255); font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(0, 150, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">君喜善设计师说，坐在大教堂里面，静默她，气势恢弘、装饰华丽、充满着雕刻、绘画、镀金的哥特式建筑风格的阶梯、威严、素洁的大厅、高贵、淡雅的肃穆、典雅的哥特式书房、幽静、用原色木料拼制的花纹多样的、历经近上千年而依然如新的地板……所有的建筑、装饰无不给人以富丽堂皇、高贵精美的感觉，其奢华程度令人咋舌。足以让我们为人类的智慧和艺术天赋感叹，君喜善设计师为热爱艺术的人创造和保存下来的艺术精品而心存感激……&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 19px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 虔诚的感觉充溢着我的心，当我们离开大教堂时，我发现我的眼睛竟然湿润了。我在想宗教的感召力可能不仅仅来自于人们原始的信仰，还有着对前辈们因虔诚而创造出的宗教艺术、因崇拜而产生出的那份庄严的神圣感的感动……</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGX0joARs4HTdCkdKGv803cTTooSJ2f8Vibic2s31qicKJ0bH36BnX9Sic6xaXGQOTEWnSticy5DJ6qDVyg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.6" data-w="800" src="/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251744565639.png" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" width="140" height="140" alt="" width="100%" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; background-color: rgb(178, 226, 129); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">一颜色：此系列采用轻快的色彩，透着一种最原始的朴素感，带来一种抛却繁华后的轻松张力；用优雅厚重紫色.宝蓝色、明黄色作为点缀色，传递出古老的声音，传统智慧在现代社会中就如同星星之火，重新被点燃活力。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; background-color: rgb(178, 226, 129); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; background-color: rgb(178, 226, 129); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">二廓形：设计师则以宽松富于空气感的H型和各种A型为主，透露出闲适自如的生活哲学。诙谐的灯笼型轮廓，简约而有趣，不对称式的立体分割，构造出灵动而多层次的轮廓看点。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; background-color: rgb(178, 226, 129); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; background-color: rgb(178, 226, 129); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">&nbsp;三面料：是彰显整体品质的关键，经典细腻的桑蚕丝材质，独家订制桑蚕丝面料；质朴却有着柔软的触感，原始、通透，又有细腻的肌理效果，呈现出层次丰富的外观效果，精致的朴素感，所注重的是材质本身的细腻和肌理以及细节的传统智慧。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 17px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; background-color: rgb(178, 226, 129); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ke4D20gXDGX0joARs4HTdCkdKGv803cTg92NL2pkyia55GQYLSa6BW1WSglbSHicn9utBx1zwamX3muJWEgVuiaxw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.5960099750623442" data-w="802" src="/minijunxishanhgnz/Data/UploadFiles/Uploads/day_170725/201707251745181117.png" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" width="140" height="140" alt="" width="100%" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">苎麻亚麻面料以前一直是作为古欧洲皇室的专用面料，尽在上层社会流通，随着苎麻面料在世界范围内广为流通，苎麻面料的优点也被人们逐渐的发掘出来。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(243, 254, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none;">苎麻的这种天然的透气性、吸湿性、清爽性.抗过敏.防静电.抗菌和排性，使其成为自由呼吸的纺织品，由于苎麻的吸湿性好，能吸收相当于自身重量 20倍的水分，所以苎麻织物手感干爽。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: STKaiti; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-kerning: none